La Esquina Criolla is a restaurant that specializes in Creole/ Puerto Rican food. Although recently open and in the process of remodeling, Â the food is excellent and plentiful as well as reasonable priced. So, don't let the unfinished interior prevent you from obtaining a rewarding palatable experience...you will returned again and again. Chef Elsie Diaz is an excellent chef that abounds in creativity. Try her custom made pastries, cakes and pies. She creates everything including the cake toppings. She also makes baked goods for people who suffer from diabetes.
